title: LF Jung/Top
body:
Just a few chill silver guys  looking for a  silver 4+ Jungler, and Top Laner to round out our roster. We play  several times a week,  and are looking to play some ranked 5 as well as just mess about in normals.

Shoot me a message on here if interested.

replies.body: S3 Jg currently in a series for S2
